-- Chelsea Submits Bid to Acquire Battersea Site for New Stadium
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-05-04T12:46:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-04/chelsea-submits-bid-to-acquire-battersea-site-for-new-stadium.html
Chelsea has submitted an offer to buy
the Battersea Power Station site in southwest  London  for
construction of a new 60,000-seat stadium, the Premier League
soccer club said on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  